  "title": "Numbers and Letters",
  "description": "This dataset contains neuroimaging data from a magnetoencephalography (MEG) experiment investigating the neural processing of numbers, letters, and false fonts presented as single items or strings. The study employs event-related experimental design with coded triggers for different stimulus categories across two runs, providing insights into visual word form processing and numerical cognition. Behavioral responses were recorded alongside MEG data. This dataset was previously accessible at ds001985 and was reuploaded due to privacy considerations.",
